Anand's preparation was excellent. He just simplified the position to a
drawish endgame} 14. Bd2 $5 Kg7 15. Qxe5+ Qxe5 16. Bc3 Qxc3+ 17. bxc3 Be6 {
we can reach such endgames from many openings. White has nothing to do; Black
