(20. Rb2 Rad8 21. Re1 (21. Rfb1 {is to illustrate what Black's intentions are}
Rd3 {[%cal Rb6d8,Rd8d3]}) 21... Rd3 22. h4 Qd4 23. Rbb1 Bg6 $44 {[%csl Ra3,Rb3]
[%cal Rf7f6,Rg6f7,Ra5a4]}) 20... Rad8 {Looking to exploit the open d file} 21.
h4 (21. Rc1) 21... Rd4 22. Rab2 (22. Kh2 Rxc4) 22... Qd8 {[%cal Rh7e4]} 23. f3
f5 $15 {[%csl Rb1,Rb2,Re4] Black regains the material and has a serious
advantage due to the passive White pieces} *

