9. e5 Qd7 10. Bh3 d4 11. O-O e6) 5. d4 e6 (5... e5) 6. e3 Bd6 7. Ne2 Ne7 8.
Nbc3 c6 9. Qd2 Nd7 10. O-O-O Qc7 11. g4 Bf7 12. h5 O-O-O {Black developed the
most natural way and got a pleasant position} 13. Kb1 Kb8 (13... g6) 14. Nc1 e5
